name: GKGameSessionError.Code
desc: Error codes for the GKGameSession domain.

items.name: case unknown
items.desc: The requested operation could not be completed due to an unknown error.

items.name: case notAuthenticated
items.desc: The requested operation could not be completed because you are not signed in to iCloud.

items.name: case sessionConflict
items.desc: The requested operation could not be completed because the session has been updated on the server, causing a conflict.

items.name: case sessionNotShared
items.desc: The requested operation could not be completed because this session has not been shared with other players.

items.name: case connectionCancelledByUser
items.desc: The requested operation could not be completed because the connection to the session was cancelled.

items.name: case connectionFailed
items.desc: The requested operation could not be completed because the session could not find other players to connect to.

items.name: case sessionHasMaxConnectedPlayers
items.desc: The requested operation could not be completed because the session has reached the maximum number of connected players.

items.name: case sendDataNotConnected
items.desc: The requested operation could not be completed because you are not connected to the session.

items.name: case sendDataNoRecipients
items.desc: The requested operation could not be completed because there are no recipients connected to session.

items.name: case sendDataNotReachable
items.desc: The requested operation could not be completed because one or more players is not reachable.

items.name: case sendRateLimitReached
items.desc: The requested operation could not be completed because you have reached the limits for save data request.

items.name: case badContainer
items.desc: The requested operation could not be completed because the iCloud container is invalid.

items.name: case cloudQuotaExceeded
items.desc: The requested operation could not be completed because the user's iCloud quota would be exceeded.

items.name: case networkFailure
items.desc: The requested operation could not be completed due to an error communicating with the server.

items.name: case cloudDriveDisabled
items.desc: The requested operation could not be completed because iCloud Drive has been disabled for the application.

items.name: case invalidSession
items.desc: The requested operation could not be completed because the Game Session does not exist or the player is not part of the game session.
